title: Will New Consoles Release Anytime Soon?
description:
PS5 Pro, Xbox Series X2. New consoles are coming. Maybe. I don’t really know. Nobody does. But I’ll talk about what I don’t know, and what nobody knows. So nobody really learns anything. Right?

Can’t wait to play Elder Scrolls VI in 8k at 240fps.
